  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "As a user, I want to be able to manually select the language used in the app, so it can be different from the one used by my operating system.\r\n\r\n### Why is this important?\r\nIt's useful for accessibility to keep language settings in-app independent from the ones in the operating system, especially making the app accessible to people who don't speak english, as not all devices allow the user to change their language from english.\r\n\r\n### Requirements:\r\n* Option to select a language\r\n* Option to inherit the language from the OS settings\r\n* Search bar to look for languages",
